## Project Structure Guide

- Edit source files only under `extension/src/**`.
- Treat `dist/**` as build output for Chrome "Load unpacked"; do not edit it directly.
- The main configuration is the MV3 manifest at [extension/manifest.json](mdc:extension/manifest.json). Keep `dist/manifest.json` in sync by copying from `extension/` when updating the build.

### Key Entry Points
- Manifest: [extension/manifest.json](mdc:extension/manifest.json)
- Background service worker: [service-worker.js](mdc:extension/src/background/service-worker.js)
- Content script: [content.js](mdc:extension/src/content/content.js)
- Injected stylesheet: [inject.css](mdc:extension/src/content/inject.css)
- Popup UI: [popup.html](mdc:extension/src/popup/popup.html), [popup.css](mdc:extension/src/popup/popup.css), [popup.js](mdc:extension/src/popup/popup.js)
- Design tokens: [variables.css](mdc:extension/src/styles/variables.css)

### Layout
```
extension/
  manifest.json
  src/
    background/service-worker.js
    content/content.js
    content/inject.css
    popup/popup.html
    popup/popup.css
    popup/popup.js
    styles/variables.css
dist/
  (build/copy of extension/ for Chrome loading)
```

